enance. Citizens are advised to check dues on the e-Sampark portal to ensure they receive these benefits.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/chandigarh-offers-property-tax-rebate-pay-by-may-31-to-save-on-taxes/130462457?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-37030/130462457.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}